OL,3,CStates of Guernsey votes to pave the
OL,4,Cway for GST
OL,6,FPoliticians decided to pass the
OL,7,Famendment by Policy and Resources
OL,8,Fwithout debate, by 20 votes to 15.
OL,10,FThis decision comes a day after
OL,11,FGuernsey's Chief Minister, Deputy
OL,12,FLyndon Trott, warned a proposed income
OL,13,Ftax rise is a "necessary" but not
OL,14,F"long-term decision".
OL,16,FThe island's most senior politician
OL,17,Fsaid that there had been no organised
OL,18,Fprotests about the income tax
OL,19,Fproposals, and he felt that public
OL,20,Fopinion was shifting while GST and
OL,21,FIncome Tax were being compared.
